query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 10 AND q.view_count <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('cs50',
'directx-11',
'eclipse-cdt',
'lotus-domino',
'ngfor',
'nvidia',
'partitioning',
'php-7',
'procedure',
'sfml',
'speech-to-text',
'turtle-graphics',
'webhooks');
